    "millsfield:images_texts": [
      "Frances\nУр\ndiscoverv\n[EMI",
      "REGAL\nTRADEMAR A E OPHONE CO, LTD. SRE G-9615\nSHEG-JOTO\nFRANCES YIP\n[EMI\n2010.029:001 b",
      "REGAL\nSTIEREI\nSREG-9615\nSRE G9615\nOMI (HK) LTD.\nFRANCES YIP\n(EMI",
      "Frances\nYip\ndiscovery\nEMI",
      "Frances Yip\nA top artist today in Hong Kong, Frances was discovered by an\ntalian priest and protessionar tutor, under whose carera guladrice\nthe rising stars talents developed. A veteran recording artist (more than\n70 sinales and albums). Frances is well known to Hong Kong's T.V.\naudiences. In 1972 and 1973 she was voted most popular singer on T.V.\nand has topped the Chinese hit parade with several of her songs.\nA magnetic ability to capture an audience plus her strong but sensitive\ninterpretations, make Frances style unique. On this discovery\nalbum she sings eleven songs ot Asia in nine languages.",
